name: Create user with different names and jobs (example #2)
fullName: Create user with different names and jobs (example #2)

steps.name: Given I have the POST endpoint
When I send a POST request with name "Alice" and job "Developer"
request ("{ method: 'POST', url: 'https://reqres.in/api/users', headers: { 'x-api-key': 'reqres-free-v1' }, body: { name: 'Alice', job: 'Developer' }, failOnStatusCode: false }")
Then the response status should be 201
Then the response should contain a user ID
